  "text": "The evidence presented here also shows that sulphated glycosaminoglycans of the extracellular matrix such as heparan sulphate are more resistant to fragmentation by reactive oxidative and reductive species. The mechanisms proposed by Davies and coworkers [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] help to rationalize this, as summarized in Scheme 3.",
